ng visited by millions of people worldwide each day.<\/p>\n<p>If your business\u2019 review ranking falls below 3-stars, then you will be missing out on more than 67% of your target audience or prospects. And that\u2019s a number you can\u2019t really afford.<\/p>\n<p>Whether you are in-charge of an online store or a local shop or both, it&#8217;s essential to make sure that you are highly-focused on delivering the best possible experience and top-notch service(s) to your target audience, prospects, or customers, which will in-turn help you avoid any negative reviews and create a great first-impression in front of your consumers.<\/p>\n<p>This brings us to our question,<br \/>\n<em>\u201cWhy are online customer reviews considered this important, and how to get more?\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Let\u2019s have a look.<\/p>\n<h2>The Importance of Online Customer Reviews<\/h2>\n<p>Here\u2019s a list of reasons why online customer reviews hold such significance:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Online Reviews Drive Purchases<\/li>\n<li>Make Brands or Businesses Look Trustworthy<\/li>\n<li>Essential to Decision Making<\/li>\n<li>Have a Major Impact on Sales<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Online Reviews Drive Purchases<\/h3>\n<p>Whether it\u2019s someone we know or a complete stranger, when we see a person praising a business\u2019 product or service online, the thought of purchasing something crosses our mind. And with more and more positive reviews we come across, our purchasing decision gets heavily influenced, and we are more inclined towards buying it.<\/p>\n<p>Thanks to online reviews, multiple businesses worldwide have managed to scale their business, as they were able to drive 200% more sales within the first few months of managing their online reputation.<\/p>\n<h3>Make Brands or Businesses Look Trustworthy<\/h3>\n<p>If you are a small or medium-sized business owner, most of your target audience won\u2019t know about you. They might not have even heard about your business before.<\/p>\n<p>It\u2019s literally the first time they will be hearing about your business or visiting your website, obviously when you run ads or achieve the top ranking on the search engines for certain keywords.<\/p>\n<p>And as we all know, \u201cFirst impression matters the most.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Before doing business with you, they will obviously want to trust you. They\u2019d want to know that they are purchasing products or services from a brand that\u2019s actually worth their time and can live up to their expectations.<\/p>\n<p>Online reviews will help you drive sales and create an outstanding impression in front of your customers. In addition to this, it will help you make sure that your business looks trustworthy, which is the most important aspect you need to care about.<\/p>\n<h3>Essential to Decision Making<\/h3>\n<p>Let&#8217;s say you have been looking forward to purchasing a headphone for a while, and finally, you hop on to Amazon and look up for a few.<\/p>\n<p>Obviously, you will come across a world full of options waiting for you to add them to your cart.<\/p>\n<p>Here, what will fuel the decision-making process is the popularity of different headphones and the number of online reviews different listings have. After looking at the specifications, you will ultimately look at the number of 3+ star reviews different headphones have.<\/p>\n<p>And based on this, you\u2019ll end up finally purchasing a headphone that suits your needs and is popular among customers.<\/p>\n<p>While reviews help businesses look trustworthy, they also heavily influence decision-making, which is why you should focus on getting a 3+ star review ranking.<\/p>\n<h3>Have a Major Impact on Sales<\/h3>\n<p>Most business owners and marketers wonder how to get customer reviews because these online pieces of text can have a major impact on sales.<\/p>\n<p>At Umbrella Local, we provide &#8220;Review Generation &amp; Online Reputation Management&#8221; services to our clients, helping them manage their reputat